{"tid":1216818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藝術課] 從現代流行音樂取得爭取民主新靈感","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:57:40.000Z","uid":15582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"868ba2bdd5b3860c3e97892743989c130a43d4b2","tid":1216818,"uid":15582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:06:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FJt7gNi3Nr4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFJt7gNi3Nr4&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmWiIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=f754e7e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FJt7gNi3Nr4</a><br />\n<br />\n邊睇片邊理解歌詞係最好嘅學習方法，　有咩唔明可以隨便問。<br />\n我撮取少部分歌詞譯俾大家，借此方便Ｄ汲收。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Human beings in a mob <br />\n人類集結成暴民<br />\nWhat's a mob to a king? What's a king to a god?  <br />\n對於國王來說，暴民算是甚麼? 對於上帝來說，國王算是甚麼?<br />\nWhat's a god to a non-believer who don't believe in anything? <br />\n對於一個不相信任何東西的無神論者，上帝又算是甚麼？<br />\nWill he make it out alive? Alright, alright, no church in the wild<br />\n他能夠繼續生存下去嘛嗎？當然，當然，荒野又怎會自生基督教義。<br />\n<br />\nTwo tattoos: one read &quot;No Apologies&quot;<br />\n身上刻上兩個紋身，其中一個寫著「不作道歉」<br />\nThe other said &quot;Love is Cursed by Monogamy&quot;<br />\n另個一個寫著「愛情被一夫一妻制所詛咒」<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">（註：現代藝術常將愛情、自由、革命放在一起討論，因為三者都有共通之處。此句歌詞是種詩化的比喻，意指　生活受到權貴者所定下的規舉所限制。）</span><br />\nIt&rsquo;s something that the pastor don&rsquo;t preach<br />\n這是傳教士不會佈道的事<br />\nIt&rsquo;s something that a teacher can&rsquo;t teach<br />\n這是教師不會教的事<br />\nWhen we die, the money we can&rsquo;t keep<br />\n當我們犧牲的時候，錢財不會隨我們而去<br />\nBut we probably spend it all cause the pain ain&rsquo;t cheap<br />\n但今天我們可能會將自己所擁有的都付出，因為要承受痛苦的代價將會非常大。<br />\nPreach<br />\n要將這佈道出去</span>"},{"pid":"7a4bb165ecb2a0a44b9b8110a9c91f885de63bce","tid":1216818,"uid":15582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fbc253a294c62595a025454ce145dc6aaa4eb1e","tid":1216818